      <h1>PeyeFasil Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="date">Last Updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>

    <p>
      PeyeFasil respects the privacy of its users and is committed to protecting personal information.
      This Privacy Policy explains how PeyeFasil collects, uses, stores, and protects user information.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>PeyeFasil may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Full name</li>
      <li>Phone number</li>
      <li>Profile information</li>
      <li>Selfie photographs</li>
      <li>Identification documents submitted for verification</li>
      <li>Transaction history</li>
      <li>Technical information required for app functionality</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>We use collected information to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Create and manage user accounts</li>
      <li>Verify user identity</li>
      <li>Process deposits, withdrawals, and transfers</li>
      <li>Improve security and prevent fraud</li>
      <li>Provide customer support</li>
      <li>Comply with applicable legal and regulatory requirements</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Identity Verification</h2>
    <p>
      Users may be required to submit a selfie and identification document to verify their identity.
      These documents are used only for account verification, fraud prevention, and security purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>Transaction Data</h2>
    <p>
      PeyeFasil may store transaction history, including deposits, withdrawals, transfers, timestamps,
      and transaction status. This information is used to provide account history and support platform security.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      PeyeFasil uses reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect user information against
      unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      PeyeFasil does not sell user personal information. Information may be shared only when necessary to:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide requested services</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      <li>Protect the security and integrity of the platform</li>
      <li>Prevent fraud or unauthorized activity</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>User Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Users may contact PeyeFasil to request access, correction, or deletion of their personal information,
      subject to legal, security, and operational requirements.
    </p>

    <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      PeyeFasil is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
      information from children under 13.
    </p>

    <h2>Business Location</h2>
    <p>
      PeyeFasil is a business primarily based in Haiti, with members of administration who may operate from
      the United States.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      PeyeFasil may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updated versions will be published on this page.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
